                {
                    "node": {
                        "created_at": "1771377683",
                        "id": "18111409603641972",
                        "text": "I\u2019ve been to listening bars all over the world, and so many of them trace their inspiration back to Japan. Sitting inside of Grandfather\u2019s for a while, it\u2019s hard not to feel like this is one of the most authentic I\u2019ve ever experienced. Five decades of history, dim lights, cigarette smoke, and music humming beneath the streets of Tokyo. For the first time, it feels like I\u2019ve reached the source.\n\nThere\u2019s still so much more of Tokyo\u2019s music scene to experience so make sure to follow Black Vinyl Stories and we\u2019ll keep exploring.\n\n#listeningbar #tokyo #blackvinylstories #recordbar"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
